e pay？"},{"pid":"31ad5a15b54e382467f6be2845ce8933da564665","tid":1668642,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43b5a2fb160b20d23dc2deeb05aa6960c4ce3933","tid":1668642,"uid":101991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b4425e475cd86bf363f165e317b6c29d6924554","tid":1668642,"uid":234220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"拎埋嗰double pay, 1月裸辭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"其實如果我十一月底辭職，通常有冇double pay？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:08:36.000Z","msg":"我唔知我公司係點，但聽過同事講話上年有個同事十二月中塔左，話點解唔捱多幾日可以攞埋double pay"},{"pid":"81636e5571c7e28962c1cbf25d2b1dfb40c07cc4","tid":1668642,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:12:45.000Z","msg":"好鍾意返工，四年轉咗兩次都係工接工<br />\n<br />\n利申：一個月1-2日SL補返"},{"pid":"8c9e07a409460ebb92dc4df0a9a2932914076bda","tid":1668642,"uid":294274,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"休息左半個月先開始搵，<br />\n一開始hea搵，一個半月內keep住interview,<br />\n無回音都好輕鬆，有回音就憑第6感估好唔好做<br />\n<br />\n搵工最緊要係鬥長命夠淡定<br />\n你有價值唔好心急乞份工<br />\n大家都玩緊卜傻瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我最近搵到份岩心水架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368b64387705620dbf020218ae8e94cbb0061e6c","tid":1668642,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81636e5571c7e28962c1cbf25d2b1dfb40c07cc4","tid":1668642,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:12:45.000Z","msg":"好鍾意返工，四年轉咗兩次都係工接工<br />\n<br />\n利申：一個月1-2日SL補返"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T15:22:50.000Z","msg":"咁勁 搵到先走？"},{"pid":"a72fa83529a5677b17ba9fec661a0305c492e516","tid":1668642,"uid":111811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"